2. His works 
Yailaya is the author of at least five more works on mathe matics and astronomy. They are : (1) Gamita-sangraha, a treatise on arithmetic, (2) Jyotișadarpaņa,“ on astronomy, (3) Kalpaval!ī, a commentary on Suryasiddhānta and (4) Kalpalata,o an extensive commentary on the Laghumanasa of Muñjāla whom Yallaya uniformly calls by his alternative name Manjula. (5) A commentary in Telugu of the Süryasiddhanta by Yallaya has also been recorded.' 
