The authorities of the Panjab University, Chandigarh, kindly permitted me to be an Editor of the present series of volumes on Āryabhata. I am very much thankful to them for providing me an opportunity to associate myself in this endeavour towards placing before the scholarly world an important chapter in the development of mathematical science in India. 
The press copy of this volume had the benefit of being read by Dr. K. S. Shukla, Deptt. of Mathematics and Astronomy, Lucknow University, who offered several valuable suggestions towards its per fection. I cannot adequately express my indebtedness to Dr Shukla in the above regard. 
